1 A BILL for an Act to amend and reenact subsection 1 of section 15.1-12-05 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to providing notice to affected property owners of a petition for the
3 annexation of property to a school district.
4 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
5 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Subsection 1 of section 15.1-12-05 of the North Dakota
6 Century Code is amended and reenacted as follows:
7 1. Upon receiving a petition for the annexation of property to a school district, the county
8 superintendent shall schedule:
9 a. Schedule and give notice of a public hearing regarding the annexation; and
10 b. Provide by certified mail notice regarding the annexation to each owner of real
11 property affected by the petition.
